title: Six dead in six days on West Bank as divisions intensify between Israel and Palestine
description: It has been another violent week in the West Bank.

title: Sixth arrest after model's body parts found in fridge and cooking pot
description: A sixth person has been arrested in connection with the murder of a Hong Kong model whose dismembered legs were found inside a fridge.

title: More than half of the world will be overweight by 2035, obesity federation warns
description: Most of the world's population - more than four billion people - will be overweight by 2035, with almost two billion (around one in four people) likely to be obese, the World Obesity Federation has warned.

title: Mother who murdered her five children euthanised at own request - on 16th anniversary of killings
description: A mother who killed her five children has been euthanised at her own request - 16 years to the day after their murders, her lawyer has said.

title: Florida man dies from brain-eating amoeba - possibly after rinsing his nose with tap water
description: A US man has died from a brain-eating amoeba - possibly after rinsing his nose with tap water, health officials have said.
